2 different pets are kept: turtle, bird
1. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person eating cranberry##8
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | avocado | cranberry |
| Pet    | turtle    | bird |

